==English==
===Etymology===
The echidna sense is derived from the verb form, English settlers in Australia would puggle to get rabbits out of holes and sometimes find an echidna.  (Reference: ''Echidnas'', Australian Broadcasting Commission Radio National Science Show, 11 November 2000, [http://www.abc.net.au/rn/science/ss/stories/s209254.htm transcript].)
